signatures.text: inline fun CharSequence.dropLastWhile( predicate: (Char) -> Boolean): CharSequence
signatures.desc: Returns a subsequence of this char sequence containing all characters except last characters that satisfy the given predicate.

signatures.text: inline fun String.dropLastWhile( predicate: (Char) -> Boolean): String
signatures.desc: Returns a string containing all characters except last characters that satisfy the given predicate.
